data.description: Welcome home to 121 9th St NE in Barberton! This spacious well maintained ranch offers over 2,500 sq ft of finished living space. Entering the home you will see plenty of windows for natural light and a warm open concept perfect for entertaining. The living room features a fireplace and opens to a lovely formal dining room. There are 3 nice sized bedrooms on the first floor and the interior has been freshly painted with a neutral color scheme. The bathroom includes a walk-in shower with a fabulous tile and marble design. You will love the updated kitchen with a full complement of stainless steel appliances, track lighting and a butcher block countertop! The kitchen overlooks the spectacular family room that has vaulted ceilings and modern lighting. The family room has sliding doors that lead to the large deck and huge backyard with a shed and smoke house. The home boasts a fully finished basement with recessed lighting, another FULL bathroom with laundry, glass block windows and ample space that could be utilized as a 4th bedroom or rec room. The garage features a convenient access keypad, built-in shelves and access to both the deck and family room. This home is truly a turnkey – there's absolutely nothing to do but move in and make it your own. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity! Schedule your private showing today!
